                    "name": "Water Travel",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "A water orm can dissolve into water, appearing only as a long, dark, serpentine stretch of water. While in this form, a water orm's swim Speed increases to 600 feet, it automatically succeeds at <a aonid=\"3\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Athletics</a> checks to <a aonid=\"39\" game-obj=\"Actions\">swim</a>, and it gains a +4 circumstance bonus to <a aonid=\"15\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Stealth</a> checks in water. A water orm can remain in this form for 8 hours, but it can't enter salt water when using this ability. A water orm can return to its normal form using a single action which has the <a aonid=\"32\" game-obj=\"Traits\">concentrate</a> trait.",
